.SH PARAMETERS
.TP \w'\f2s\fP\ \f2t\fP\ \f2r\fP\ \f2q\fP\ \ 'u 
\f2s\fP, \f2t\fP, \f2r\fP, \f2q\fP
Specify \f2s\fP, \f2t\fP, \f2r\fP, and \f2q\fP  texture coordinates.
Not all parameters are present in all forms of the command.
